betterquesting:10.desc:8: Setup basic farms and harvest them automatically using an Ender IO Farming Station, a MineFactory Reloaded Planter & Harvester, or an Ender IO Addons AgriCraft Farming Station. Boost the growth speed of your crops by mutating them to 10/10/10s, craft an Imaginary Time Block so your crops grow insanely fast, and create Magical Crops that can produce all types of different materials!
